---
// Canonical intro copy — keep in sync with jalxp.github.io/index.md.
---
<div class="intro">
  <div class="intro-kicker">// readme.md</div>
  <p class="intro-lead">
    Hey, I'm João. <span class="acc">iOS engineer by day, chronic tinkerer by night.</span>
  </p>
  <p>
    I've spent the last five years building mobile apps — sweating the details on
    architecture, performance, and the kind of UX that feels obvious in hindsight.
    When I'm not pushing pixels and protocols on iOS, I'm usually down a rabbit hole:
    running way too many containers on my homelab, poking at network traffic with a
    wardriving Pi, or finally building that top-down RTS I've been meaning to get to
    since forever.
  </p>
  <p>
    This site is where I write things down. Tutorials when I've figured something out
    worth sharing. Deep dives when a topic earns it. The occasional rant about
    something obscure I can't stop thinking about.
  </p>
  <p class="intro-sig">
    No posting schedule. No content calendar. Just things I find interesting, written
    well enough that you might too.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .intro {
    padding: 22px 24px 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--panel), var(--panel-2));
    position: relative;
  }
  .intro::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; left: 0; top: 16px; bottom: 16px; width: 3px;
    background: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--accent);
  }
  .intro-kicker {
    font-family: var(--mono-ui);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: .2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .intro p {
    font-family: var(--mono-body);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    max-width: 64ch;
  }
  .intro-lead {
    font-size: 16px !important;
    color: var(--ink) !important;
  }
  .intro-lead .acc {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-shadow: 0 0 6px color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent) 40%, transparent);
  }
  .intro-sig {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-muted) !important;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--line);
    padding-top: 14px;
  }
</style>
